" If correct, press \\\"ENTER\\\", 1 to add keywords and 2 to remove "
"keywords: "
msgstr ""
" 올바르면 \\\"ENTER\\\"를 누르고, 키워드를 추가하려면 1, 제거하려면 2를 누르"
"십시오: "

#: modules/template.am:282
msgid " URL must contain (\\\"x64\\\", \\\"x86_64\\\"... or leave blank): "
